English:
Tuck an ally girl into Kisume's bucket for %duration% seconds. In this state, 「Sarayashiki's Burning Out」will deal double damage, but the health of the ally tucked will be set to %max_health%%% of the max as well.
The ally tucked will be ejected in next four situations:
-Kisume dies;
-Time is up;
-Kisume ejects her;
-She gets out by herself.
